---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 310
  - Title: Theologia Germanica
    Location: L
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=The Divine Imprint in Manifestation
  - 583
---
This world is verily an outer court of the Eternal, or of Eternity,
and specially whatever in Time, or any temporal things or creatures,
manifesteth or remindeth us of God or Eternity; for the creatures are
a guide and a path unto God and Eternity.
